#~ msgstr "提交反馈时出错。请稍后再试。"

#: src/components/tile.tsx:275
msgid "Eta Aquariids Meteor Shower"
msgstr "宝瓶座η流星雨"

#: src/hooks/seasonal-events/earth-day.tsx:159
msgid "Even small choices — repairing, reusing, conserving, or simply walking a familiar trail — reflect its underlying spirit."
msgstr "即使是很小的选择——修理、再利用、节约，或只是走一条熟悉的小径——都体现了它的精神底色。"

#: src/hooks/seasonal-events/valentines.tsx:103
msgid "Even today, paper hearts and quiet notes continue the tradition of deliberate kindness."
msgstr "直到今天，纸心与悄悄写下的短笺仍延续着那份刻意的善意。"

#: src/hooks/seasonal-events/christmas.tsx:78
msgid "Evergreens, candles, bells, and stars echo a shared theme drawn from those early traditions: light enduring through the darkest part of the year in the cultures where the holiday first formed."
msgstr "常青植物、蜡烛、铃铛与星星，呼应着早期传统中的共同主题：在一年最黑暗的时段里，光依然延续。"

#: src/components/weather-alert.tsx:52
msgid "Extreme UV for the next {durationOfExtremeUv} hours"
msgstr "接下来 {durationOfExtremeUv} 小时内的极端紫外线"

#: src/components/weather-alert.tsx:49
